  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>甘い物の食べ過ぎは身体によくない。
今後は、バランスの良い
食生活を心がけてくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eating so many sweet things isn't good
for your health. From now on, you should
dedicate yourself to having good,
balanced eating habits.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>くっ、なぜ僕が
説教などされなければならない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kh. Why am I the one who
needs to be preached at?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ピーチパイに……出会えなかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I didn't... encounter any peach pie...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん、
このクレープうめぇな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yup. This crepe is awesome.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お、こっちのパフェもいけるじゃねぇか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, this parfait over here looks good, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい、どういう事だ！
お前の相棒もかなり食べているぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, what is the meaning of this?!
Your partner is eating a bunch of them, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うっ、ユーリ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahh... Yuri...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
